Odoo Select Product UOM In Website

This app allows you to configure product-wise multi-uom. and on the website users can buy products in any UOM as per the configuration.

Easy to use and setup.
Selected product UOM automatically reflects in odoo backend orders.
You can select UOM on website product page.
You can set different UOM on same product. Product price automatically change as per variant and uom.
You can see UOM in cart page, confirmation page and thank you page when you are placing order.

Go to the setting >> Users & Company >> Users, and active "manage multiple unit of measurement" group. as mentioned in screenshot.

Open any product and under the sales tab you can configure setting of UOM.

Now you can open that product in website and you will see option for select UOM.

You can select UOM and quantity and pricing will be change accordingly and in further process the same UOM will being forwarded.
